  background-color: #e0ffff;\n    padding: 0px;\n    margin: 0;\n  }\n\n  .container {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 250px;\n    justify-content: center;\n    padding-bottom: 200px;\n  }\n\n  .card {\n    background-color: #2abec2;\n    color: white;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    width: 300px;\n    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n    border: none;\n    transition: transform 0.3s;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  .card:hover {\n    transform: scale(1.05);\n    background-color: #00305e;\n  }\n\n  .card:hover .card-header {\n    background-color: #00305e;\n  }\n\n  .card-header {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    align-items: center;\n    height: 100px;\n    background-color: #2abec2;\n  }\n\n  .highlight {\n    background-color: white;\n    color: #2abec2;\n    padding: 6px 12px;\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    font-size: 16px;\n  }\n\n  .card-body {\n    padding: 20px;\n  }\n\n  .card-body h2 {\n    margin-top: 0;\n    font-size: 20px;\n  }\n\n  .card-body ul {\n    padding-left: 20px;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    font-weight: normal;\n  }\n\n  .card-body ul li {\n    margin-bottom: 8px;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 900px) {\n    .container {\n      flex-direction: column;\n      align-items: center;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><br>\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"card\">\n<div class=\"card-header\">\n<div class=\"highlight\">18 - 30 años</div>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card-body\">\n<h2>Entrenamiento de Alto Rendimiento</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Rutinas de fuerza e hipertrofia</li>\n<li>Entrenamientos HIIT y funcionales</li>\n<li>Alta frecuencia semanal</li>\n<li>Enfoque en desarrollo muscular</li>\n<li>Complemento con cardio intenso</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card\">\n<div class=\"card-header\">\n<div class=\"highlight\">30 - 45 años</div>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"card-body\">\